{"tid":1933230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油塘男遭20黑漢狂斬重創命危 5兇徒乘車欲逃被捕","createTime":"2020-03-19T07:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T09:23:17.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ff9df3ee43172d6072d60eee7555bb4eec7e28","tid":1933230,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"【12:30】消息稱，被捕兇徒疑有黑幫新義安背景<br />\n【09:20】傷者目前留醫伊利沙伯醫院，情況危殆；警方東九龍反黑組接手跟進案件<br />\n油塘發生斬人血案。晚上8時許，姓李61歲男子與朋友在鯉魚門吃飯，其間20多名大漢突然現身撲出，有人向事主揮刀追斬。事主拔足狂奔，並往鯉魚門牌坊方向逃走，但走避不及，遭人斬傷身中多刀，血流如注。<br />\n<br />\n歹徒逞兇後跳上至少5架接應車輛離開，湊巧警車趕至，在附近崇信街發現一輛可疑私家車，經調查相信車上5名男子與案有關，將他們制服拘捕。疑犯年齡介乎21至28歲，案件由東九龍反黑組接手跟進，事主亦送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救。<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/gDa2Q-DyxMuzPgnNHCBaQDGezZ4=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/GIB2EFA2DWOZTM3CZR5ZVKCIYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FgDa2Q-DyxMuzPgnNHCBaQDGezZ4%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FGIB2EFA2DWOZTM3CZR5ZVKCIYE.jpg&h=f94e6e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事後，讀者徐先生向《蘋果》提供兩條片段，片中見到事主與朋友往牌坊方向逃走，身後尾隨十多名大漢，其間更有多名大漢手持鐵通及利刀，從一架七人車落車尾隨追斬。他指事主與朋友逃至牌坊附近的的士站，意圖登上的士離開，惟大批刀手趕至，甚至有一輛私家車駛至截停的士，事主只好落車逃命，惟他最終走避不及被斬傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200319/3F5E4OOBXF7SFOFCRKB4I7HQ4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200319%2F3F5E4OOBXF7SFOFCRKB4I7HQ4A%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=a721c9a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200319%2F3F5E4OOBXF7SFOFCRKB4I7HQ4A%2F&h=ab2ce630\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200319/3F5E4OOBXF7SFOFCRKB4I7HQ4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n廿個斬一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291bc1212ffbeefd98a321c01a3b59c4b1521d0d","tid":1933230,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"未有事先知會黑警<br />\n所以走唔甩"},{"pid":"471ddfba65c3b140c46239dd49518630cf5aad08","tid":1933230,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:30:45.000Z","msg":"睇片右面個男人好MAN<br />\n保護坐個女人<br />\n想比佢屌了"},{"pid":"66aca5bae546fe75942690fb9735f411e50f339b","tid":1933230,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AXsrvZZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAXsrvZZ.gif&h=9e04ae04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce97ae8f51f9a38b216f0750b703d43090c16ed1","tid":1933230,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:32:00.000Z","msg":"廿個咁明目張膽, 夾定架? 等你斬完先出黎"},{"pid":"2b61b948e1fbe19f92c89e81cfbc859117c5088f","tid":1933230,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"黑社會咁撚疊馬又唔見你斬黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe1f0458c1b11b112fabcf1e251eabc15693715","tid":1933230,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fc68bf747ac868f697a652563916e6c615b5a75","tid":1933230,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"廿個斬一個 拉到5個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4341b624051fb6b4da548bac58f83ba82185fce9","tid":1933230,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fc68bf747ac868f697a652563916e6c615b5a75","tid":1933230,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:36:34